===Noun===
{{en-noun|-|s}}

# A plant of certain species of the genus ''[[Brassica]]'', or of related genera (especially ''[[Sinapis alba]]'', in the family [[Brassicaceae]], with yellow [[flower]]s, and linear [[seed]] [[pod]]s.
# Powder or paste made from seeds of the mustard plant, and used as a [[condiment]] or a [[spice]].
#: ''When the waitress brought the food I asked her if she had any Dijon '''mustard'''.''
# Dark [[yellow]] [[color|colour]], the colour of mustard.
#: {{color panel|F2B73F}}
# The [[tomalley]] of a [[crab]], which resembles the condiment.

